        <h2><a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.windycitygridiron.com&#x2F;2015&#x2F;2&#x2F;19&#x2F;8069139&#x2F;2015-nfl-combine-chicago-bears-nfl-draft" data-analytics-link="hero">2015 NFL Combine: Schedule for 2/19 (Open Thread)</a></h2>
